description:
On today’s show, Emily is answering emails and helping you use your sexual confidence as a way to boost your self confidence.

Emily helps listeners understand the importance of “repair” in a long-term relationship, the benefits of trying out a new “persona” during sex, even if it’s completely different than who you really are, why there’s never been a better time to be single, and the key reasons why people cheat – and it might not be what you think.
